# F23 data-quality DETAIL report carries KeyRecordNumber + offending raw values
# (row-level patient data) — never commit.  The aggregate models/dataquality_summary.json
# (counts only, no identifiers) IS tracked.
models/dataquality_report.json

# schema/raw_profile.json is a generated column profile.  Though it stores no
# patient rows, its identifier-column aggregates leak real medical-record numbers
# (IDNumber min/max/median) and record-entry timestamps (STAMP) — never commit.
# scripts/01_profile_raw.py now redacts those columns; regenerate locally as needed.
schema/raw_profile.json

