# serena / headroom local scratch.  The nested .serena/.gitignore (tracked,
# committed as-is per CLAUDE.md) ignores /cache + /project.local.yml; this
# repo-root line covers the one path it omits.  Serena's memory system is
# disabled globally (the AGENT_NOTES system is the sole memory store), so
# .serena/memories/ stays empty — ignored here as a safety net.  Tracked .serena
# files: project.yml (LSP config) + .gitignore.
.serena/memories/
